(4, 5, 'regina-settings', 'a:67:{s:34:\"regina_lite_features_general_title\";s:8:\"About Us\";s:40:\"regina_lite_features_general_description\";s:470:\"VSPS is one of the premier institutions of not only Uttar Pradesh but also in India.It has about 200 well qualified teachers. Almost all of them are Ph.D,many of them are working on minor and major projects sanctioned by various funding agencies.Some of them have been on academic assignments abroad. About 70% of them are engaged in research work in various departments. Many of them have contributed articles and research papers to national and international journals.\";s:40:\"regina_lite_features_general_button_text\";s:12:\"Our Services\";s:39:\"regina_lite_features_general_button_url\";s:1:\"#\";s:35:\"regina_lite_features_feature1_title\";s:0:\"\";s:41:\"regina_lite_features_feature1_description\";s:0:\"\";s:39:\"regina_lite_features_feature1_buttonurl\";s:0:\"\";s:35:\"regina_lite_features_feature2_title\";s:0:\"\";s:41:\"regina_lite_features_feature2_description\";s:0:\"\";s:39:\"regina_lite_features_feature2_buttonurl\";s:0:\"\";s:35:\"regina_lite_features_feature3_title\";s:0:\"\";s:41:\"regina_lite_features_feature3_description\";s:0:\"\";s:39:\"regina_lite_features_feature3_buttonurl\";s:0:\"\";s:35:\"regina_lite_features_feature4_title\";s:0:\"\";s:41:\"regina_lite_features_feature4_description\";s:0:\"\";s:39:\"regina_lite_features_feature4_buttonurl\";s:0:\"\";s:33:\"regina_lite_ourteam_general_title\";s:13:\"WHAT WE OFFER\";s:39:\"regina_lite_ourteam_general_description\";s:131:\"We offer various  services  like playground  for  playing  student  computer lab physics lab chemistry lab &amp; biology lab.\";s:37:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember1_image\";s:61:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/13.jpg\";s:36:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember1_name\";s:10:\"Playground\";s:40:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember1_position\";s:22:\"playground for student\";s:43:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember1_description\";s:78:\"We have a school playground for playing student in Games period or Lunch Time.\";s:41:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember1_buttonurl\";s:1:\"#\";s:37:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember2_image\";s:78:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Lab1-e1574676500349.jpg\";s:36:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember2_name\";s:12:\"Computer Lab\";s:40:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember2_position\";s:9:\"computers\";s:43:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember2_description\";s:113:\"Students, faculty and staff have access to the computer labs, which provide the tools and technologies to produce\";s:41:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember2_buttonurl\";s:1:\"#\";s:37:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember3_image\";s:63:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/lab2.jpg\";s:36:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember3_name\";s:11:\"Physics Lab\";s:40:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember3_position\";s:21:\"biological instrument\";s:43:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember3_description\";s:183:\"Physics laboratory is a place where experiments of Physics are carried out. As we know physics is that branch of science where experimentation is an integral part of the core subject.\";s:41:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember3_buttonurl\";s:1:\"#\";s:37:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember4_image\";s:65:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/lab4-1.jpg\";s:36:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember4_name\";s:11:\"Biology Lab\";s:40:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember4_position\";s:18:\"Biology instrument\";s:43:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember4_description\";s:152:\"The Biology laboratory provides the students with all sorts of facilities. The laboratory is quite spacious and is creatively decorated by the students.\";s:41:\"regina_lite_ourteam_teammember4_buttonurl\";s:1:\"#\";s:39:\"regina_lite_testimonials_general_image1\";s:78:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20190407-WA0025.jpg\";s:39:\"regina_lite_testimonials_general_image2\";s:78:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20180520-WA0039.jpg\";s:39:\"regina_lite_testimonials_general_image3\";s:78:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20180526-WA0058.jpg\";s:39:\"regina_lite_testimonials_general_image4\";s:80:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20180520-WA0036-1.jpg\";s:49:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial1_description\";s:310:\"Excellent. We wouldn’t change anything about it. I would like to see a course on study skills as in effective note taking, preparation for exams, time management. The teachers do such a great job of managing the student’s time I worry they won’t be prepared for being neglected when they get to college..\";s:43:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial1_image\";s:65:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg\";s:42:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial1_name\";s:3:\"MR.\";s:46:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial1_position\";s:7:\"Manager\";s:49:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial2_description\";s:222:\"As a Principal, I invite all students of the College to communicate directly with me, if they have any problem.The college can achieve new heights and better insights with active and productive support of the old students.\";s:43:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial2_image\";s:65:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg\";s:42:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial2_name\";s:3:\"MR.\";s:46:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial2_position\";s:9:\"Principle\";s:49:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial3_description\";s:174:\"<p class=\"testimonial\">Great school to study for. Pay structure is less; Teachers are great, kids are warm and friendly. This is the best school.</p>\n<p class=\"overview\"></p>\";s:43:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial3_image\";s:65:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg\";s:42:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial3_name\";s:3:\"MR.\";s:46:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial3_position\";s:7:\"Cashier\";s:49:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial4_description\";s:287:\"<p class=\"testimonial\">At V.S. Public school, we are hope to create are atmosphere of reverence for education and a healthy environment where work, sports and co-curricular activities will mould our students and spur them on to be the brightest and the best.</p>\n<p class=\"overview\"></p>\";s:43:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial4_image\";s:65:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg\";s:42:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial4_name\";s:3:\"MR.\";s:46:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial4_position\";s:18:\"Accountant Manager\";s:49:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial5_description\";s:398:\"<p class=\"testimonial\">Effective Transportation Management, Our transportation management system enables the admin office to efficiently manage the transportation force owned by the schools, In terms of maintaining the vehicle details, vehicle documentation, student details, Support staff details, Time of arrival and departure, route details, staff details and so on.</p>\n<p class=\"overview\"></p>\";s:43:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial5_image\";s:65:\"http://localhost/skool_1_.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg\";s:42:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial5_name\";s:3:\"MR.\";s:46:\"regina_lite_testimonials_testimonial5_position\";s:17:\"Transport Manager\";s:31:\"regina_lite_speak_general_title\";s:22:\"Speak with our doctors\";s:37:\"regina_lite_speak_general_description\";s:117:\"We offer various services lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt.\";s:35:\"regina_lite_speak_general_buttonurl\";s:1:\"#\";s:35:\"regina_lite_subheader_features_show\";i:0;s:30:\"regina_lite_speak_general_show\";i:0;}'),
