(287, 1, '2019-11-27 10:57:16', '2019-11-27 10:57:16', '<span style=\"color: #008080;\">About Us</span>\r\n\r\nVSPS is one of the premier institutions of not only Uttar Pradesh but also in India.It has about 200 well qualified teachers. Almost all of them are Ph.D,many of them are working on minor and major projects sanctioned by various funding agencies.Some of them have been on academic assignments abroad. About 70% of them are engaged in research work in various departments. Many of them have contributed articles and research papers to national and international journals.\r\n<h3>Latest News</h3>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-286 size-medium\" src=\"http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/screenshot-300x165.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"165\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In the winter trimester, our attention turns to The All School Production, an extravaganza of singing, dancing and acting.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h4>Honour</h4>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-286\" src=\"http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/screenshot-300x165.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"165\" />\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">\r\n\r\nIn the winter trimester, our attention turns to The All School Production, an extravaganza of singing, dancing and acting.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7\">\r\n<h4>Honour</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nLatest News\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993300;\">                                               August 10, 2019</span>\r\n\r\nCircular of Eid<span style=\"color: #993300;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993300;\">                                               July 22, 2019</span>\r\n\r\nCircular of Monsoon Season\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #993300;\">                                               July 18, 2019</span>\r\n\r\nCircular of Invitation to IEW\r\n\r\n<hr />