(480, 1, '2019-12-03 08:02:30', '2019-12-03 08:02:30', 'Services Section<br><br>Sho/Hide Services Section: 0<br>Section Title: About Us<br>Section Description: VSPS is one of the premier institutions of not only Uttar Pradesh but also in India.It has about 200 well qualified teachers. Almost all of them are Ph.D,many of them are working on minor and major projects sanctioned by various funding agencies.Some of them have been on academic assignments abroad. About 70% of them are engaged in research work in various departments. Many of them have contributed articles and research papers to national and international journals.<br>Section Button Text: Our Services<br>Section Button URL: #<br>Service 1 Title: <br>Service 1 Description: <br>Service 1 Button URL: <br>Service 2 Title: <br>Service 2 Description: <br>Service 2 Button URL: <br>Service 3 Title: <br>Service 3 Description: <br>Service 3 Button URL: <br>Service 4 Title: <br>Service 4 Description: <br>Service 4 Button URL: <br><br>Our Team Section<br><br>Section Title: WHAT WE OFFER<br>Section Description: We offer various  services  like playground  for  playing  student  computer lab physics lab chemistry lab &amp; biology lab.<br>Member 1 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/13.jpg<br>Member 1 Name: Playground<br>Member 1 Description: We have a school playground for playing student in Games period or Lunch Time.<br>Member 1 Button URL: #<br>Member 2 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Lab1-e1574676500349.jpg<br>Member 2 Name: Computer Lab<br>Member 2 Description: Students, faculty and staff have access to the computer labs, which provide the tools and technologies to produce<br>Member 2 Button URL: #<br>Member 3 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/lab2.jpg<br>Member 3 Name: Physics Lab<br>Member 3 Description: Physics laboratory is a place where experiments of Physics are carried out. As we know physics is that branch of science where experimentation is an integral part of the core subject.<br>Member 3 Button URL: #<br>Member 4 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/lab3.jpg<br>Member 4 Name: Chemistry Lab<br>Member 4 Description: The chemistry laboratory provides a central chemistry lab structure<br>Member 4 Button URL: #<br><br>Testimonials Section<br><br>Gallery Image 1: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20180521-WA0035.jpg<br>Gallery Image 2: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20180526-WA0031.jpg<br>Gallery Image 3: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20180526-WA0086.jpg<br>Gallery Image 4: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG-20180526-WA0069.jpg<br>Testimonial 1 Content: Excellent. We wouldn’t change anything about it. I would like to see a course on study skills as in effective note taking, preparation for exams, time management. The teachers do such a great job of managing the student’s time I worry they won’t be prepared for being neglected when they get to college..<br>Testimonial 1 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/director.jpg<br>Testimonial 1 Person Name: MR. ARUN MISHRA<br>Testimonial 1 Person Position: Manager<br>Testimonial 2 Content: As a Principal, I invite all students of the College to communicate directly with me, if they have any problem.The college can achieve new heights and better insights with active and productive support of the old students.<br>Testimonial 2 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/principal.jpg<br>Testimonial 2 Person Name: MR. PRABHUNATH UPADHYAY<br>Testimonial 2 Person Position: Principle<br>Testimonial 3 Content: <p class=\"testimonial\">Great school to study for. Pay structure is less; Teachers are great, kids are warm and friendly. This is the best school.</p>\n<p class=\"overview\"></p><br>Testimonial 3 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg<br>Testimonial 3 Person Name: MR. DHEERAJ DUBAY<br>Testimonial 3 Person Position: Cashier<br>Testimonial 4 Content: <p class=\"testimonial\">At V.S. Public school, we are hope to create are atmosphere of reverence for education and a healthy environment where work, sports and co-curricular activities will mould our students and spur them on to be the brightest and the best.</p>\n<p class=\"overview\"></p><br>Testimonial 4 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg<br>Testimonial 4 Person Name: MR. NITESH TIWARI<br>Testimonial 4 Person Position: Accountant Manager<br>Testimonial 5 Content: <p class=\"testimonial\">Effective Transportation Management, Our transportation management system enables the admin office to efficiently manage the transportation force owned by the schools, In terms of maintaining the vehicle details, vehicle documentation, student details, Support staff details, Time of arrival and departure, route details, staff details and so on.</p>\n<p class=\"overview\"></p><br>Testimonial 5 Image: http://localhost/skool_1.0/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/dummy1.jpg<br>Testimonial 5 Person Name: MR. PRAVESH MISHRA<br>Testimonial 5 Person Position: Transport Manager<br><br>Recent Works Section<br><br>Sho/Hide Section: 0<br>Section Title: Speak with our doctors<br>Section Description: We offer various services lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt.<br>Section Button URL: #<br>', 'Regina Settings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-03 08:02:30', '2019-12-03 08:02:30', '', 5, 'http://localhost/skool_1.0/2019/12/03/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
